<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="accompany-vt">accompany <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /əˈkʌmpəni/    美 /əˈkʌmpəni/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>陪伴；伴随：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Children under 14 must be accompanied by an adult.
不满14岁的孩子必须有大人陪同。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Thunder usually accompanies lightning. 
雷声常常伴随着闪电。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>为...伴奏：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Mary sang and I <strong>accompanied</strong> her on the piano.<strong> on</strong>
玛丽唱歌，我弹钢琴伴奏。</p></div></div>